    • 方法详细资料

      • getEventType

        public int getEventType()
        Gets the event type.
        返回:
        either CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_STARTING, CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_SWITCHING, CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_UNLOCKING, CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_UNLOCKED, CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_STOPPING or CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_STOPPED for all apps; for apps targeting car version CarVersion.VERSION_CODES#TIRAMISU_1 or higher, it could be new types added on later releases, such as CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_CREATED, CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_REMOVED and possibly others.

      • getUserId

        public int getUserId()
        Gets the id of the user whose event is being reported.

      • getUserHandle

        public UserHandle getUserHandle()
        Gets the handle of the user whose event is being reported.

      • getPreviousUserId

        public int getPreviousUserId()
        Gets the id of the user being switched from.

        This method returns UserHandle#USER_NULL for all event types but CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_SWITCHING.

      • getPreviousUserHandle

        public UserHandle getPreviousUserHandle()
        Gets the handle of the user being switched from.

        This method returns null for all event types but CarUserManager.USER_LIFECYCLE_EVENT_TYPE_SWITCHING.
